1. Executive Summary
-------------------
EthicSupply is an innovative supply chain optimization tool that revolutionizes how businesses select and manage their suppliers. By combining artificial intelligence with ethical considerations, the application helps organizations make data-driven decisions that balance cost efficiency with social responsibility and environmental sustainability.

2. Business Overview
------------------
The modern supply chain faces complex challenges:
• Rising costs and market volatility
• Increasing environmental regulations
• Growing demand for ethical business practices
• Need for sustainable operations
• Pressure for transparent decision-making

EthicSupply addresses these challenges by providing:
• Comprehensive supplier evaluation
• Ethical compliance monitoring
• Environmental impact assessment
• Cost optimization
• Transparent decision-making process

3. Application Purpose
